text1: The Water Network Tool for Resilience (WNTR) was developed by researchers at the University of Colorado Boulder's Mortenson Center in Global Engineering.
text2: To help communities and their drinking water utilities, researchers from EPA and the Sandia National Laboratories developed the Water Network Tool for Resilience (WNTR)
